title: Decorating Pots: 25 Creative Projects
description:
Decorating Pots: 25 Creative Projects To Make by Stephanie Donaldson (Author)

Overview: Turn commonplace red clay flowerpots around the house into eye-catching additions to your decor, and brighten any room, express any mood, or celebrate any holiday. From the 25 basic designs, using ordinary tools and materials like gift wrap, paint, buttons, twigs, bottle tops, and seashells, you can give any plant that special setting for any space or occasion. Plus, you can adapt the projects to customize pots to your own original designs. A Selection of BOMC's Country Book Club. 128 pages, 150 color illus
